    public interface DefaultOutput<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>
extends To<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>, Consume<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>
    Optional step of the EMBuilder that allow to specify a default value if the result of the Transformer step is null.

    Next step: To
